ECHOS APP MVP
Description
An app that will allow the user to add quotes(quote, author(preset to self)), those quotes will be shown at a set interval via notifications to the user. The app will allow the user to delete their quotes as well. 

Screens
	MAIN
	Shows a vertical list of quotes. A + sign to add a quote, a - sign to delete a quote or multiple quotes. Shows a gear icon for configuration.

	ADD QUOTE DIALOG
	Shows a text field for the quote and a text field for the author(preset to self).

Names
	Echos
	Quotes
	Echo

		
